  <title>libmwaw-&libmwaw-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libmwaw package contains import filters for some old Mac text documents
      (like MacWrite and ClarisWorks) based on top of libwpd.
    </para>

